Rating: 3
I followed the recipe almost exactly, except I used vegetable broth instead of chicken broth. I thought it was very good. It definitely needs quite a bit of salt and pepper - the recipe doesn't indicate any, and I could see how it would be bland with no salt and pepper. My only issue was more of a presentation thing. Using milk instead of something heavier like cream or half and half causes the soup to look a bit curdled if you let it sit and simmer. Not a huge deal, but?? I will probably make it again. I liked the mace.

Rating: 4
I love this soup! I made it exactly to recipe and took it to a party where it got excellent reviews. For me the mace is the highlight of the soup. Yes, it is mild, but so very good!

