Rating: 3
Satisfying creamy soup, and so healthy! I used red cabbage, and the soup turned out a lovely violet color that looked very inviting in pale turquoise bowls. I also substituted vegetable broth for the chicken broth. I wouldn't increase the mace, since the cabbage flavor is delicate. I might try olive oil instead of butter next time.

